Madam Kama Marg, Martyr Rajguru Chowk,
Reference: - The Maharashtra Regulation of Transfer of Government Employees and Prevention of Delays in the Performance of Government Duties Act, 2005
General Administration Department Notification No. SRV-2021 / Q. No.49 / Karyakarta-12, D. 14.07.2021
3. Ma. State Election Commission No. Rania - 2025 / NAP - 2025 /
Code of Conduct / No.684 / Ka-6, D. 11.119.2025.

As per the provisions of Section 4 (4) w.e.f. 4 (5) of the Maharashtra Regulation of Transfer of Government Employees and Prevention of Delay in discharge of Government Duties Act, 2005, the following officers of the cadre of Deputy Collectors are appointed in front of their name for administrative reasons in Column No. The post indicated in section 4 is being posted with the approval of the competent authority in the interest of public service and administrative convenience.
The said orders are being issued with the approval of the competent authority.
x. This Government Order is available on the website of the Government of Maharashtra www.maharashtra.gov.in.
table_trans: Orders regarding their appointment are being made and will be issued separately.
